fields.name: Badminton Singles (Boys)
fields.description: Individual badminton tournament for boys. Players compete one-on-one in singles matches showcasing agility, reflexes, and strategic shot placement.

fields.name: Badminton Singles (Girls)
fields.description: Individual badminton tournament for girls. Players compete one-on-one in singles matches showcasing agility, reflexes, and strategic shot placement.

fields.name: Badminton Doubles (Boys)
fields.description: Doubles badminton tournament for boys. Teams of two players coordinate to cover the court, combining power and precision in fast-paced rallies.

fields.name: Badminton Doubles (Girls)
fields.description: Doubles badminton tournament for girls. Teams of two players coordinate to cover the court, combining power and precision in fast-paced rallies.

fields.name: Carrom Singles (Boys)
fields.description: Individual carrom board tournament for boys. Players demonstrate precision and strategy to pocket carrom men using the striker on a wooden board.

fields.name: Carrom Singles (Girls)
fields.description: Individual carrom board tournament for girls. Players demonstrate precision and strategy to pocket carrom men using the striker on a wooden board.

fields.name: Carrom Doubles (Boys)
fields.description: Doubles carrom tournament for boys. Pairs work together in turns, strategizing to pocket their pieces while blocking opponents.

fields.name: Carrom Doubles (Girls)
fields.description: Doubles carrom tournament for girls. Pairs work together in turns, strategizing to pocket their pieces while blocking opponents.

fields.name: Chess (Boys)
fields.description: Individual chess tournament for boys. Players engage in tactical battles on the 64-square board, demonstrating strategic thinking and foresight.

fields.name: Chess (Girls)
fields.description: Individual chess tournament for girls. Players engage in tactical battles on the 64-square board, demonstrating strategic thinking and foresight.

fields.name: Table Tennis Singles (Boys)
fields.description: Individual table tennis tournament for boys. Fast-paced singles matches testing reflexes, spin control, and quick decision-making skills.

fields.name: Table Tennis Singles (Girls)
fields.description: Individual table tennis tournament for girls. Fast-paced singles matches testing reflexes, spin control, and quick decision-making skills.

fields.name: Table Tennis Doubles (Boys)
fields.description: Doubles table tennis tournament for boys. Partners alternate shots in high-speed rallies, requiring coordination and synchronized gameplay.

fields.name: Table Tennis Doubles (Girls)
fields.description: Doubles table tennis tournament for girls. Partners alternate shots in high-speed rallies, requiring coordination and synchronized gameplay.

fields.name: Box Cricket (Boys)
fields.description: Indoor box cricket tournament for boys. Modified cricket format played in a confined space with unique rules, emphasizing quick reflexes and innovative shots.

fields.name: Box Cricket (Girls)
fields.description: Indoor box cricket tournament for girls. Modified cricket format played in a confined space with unique rules, emphasizing quick reflexes and innovative shots.

fields.name: Dodgeball (Girls)
fields.description: Team dodgeball tournament for girls. Teams throw balls to eliminate opponents while dodging incoming throws, combining agility, teamwork, and quick reflexes.

fields.name: Cricket Over-arm (Boys)
fields.description: Traditional over-arm cricket tournament for boys. Full 11-player teams compete in standard cricket format with batting, bowling, and fielding.

fields.name: Tug of War (Boys)
fields.description: Team tug of war competition for boys. Teams pull on opposite ends of a rope, testing collective strength, coordination, and endurance.

fields.name: Kabaddi (Boys)
fields.description: Traditional kabaddi tournament for boys. Raiders tag opponents while holding breath (chanting 'kabaddi'), while defenders work to restrain them. A test of stamina, strategy, and strength.

fields.name: Kabaddi (Girls)
fields.description: Traditional kabaddi tournament for girls. Raiders tag opponents while holding breath (chanting 'kabaddi'), while defenders work to restrain them. A test of stamina, strategy, and strength.

fields.name: Volleyball (Boys)
fields.description: Team volleyball tournament for boys. Teams of 6 players spike, block, and dig to score points over the net, requiring coordination and athletic prowess.

fields.name: Throwball (Girls)
fields.description: Team throwball tournament for girls. Players throw the ball over the net to score points, combining elements of volleyball with throwing techniques.

fields.name: Kho-Kho (Girls)
fields.description: Traditional kho-kho tournament for girls. Chasers and defenders alternate in this fast-paced tag game requiring speed, agility, and strategic positioning.

fields.name: Football (Boys)
fields.description: Team football tournament for boys. Standard 11-a-side soccer matches with teams competing to score goals through passing, dribbling, and teamwork.
